You will have to submit a medical fitness certificate on or before the specified joining date.
You will be entitled to avail leave only once in a year.
You need to handover the original Degree / Diploma Certificate as soon as you join the company.
In case of Resignation you need to give us 3 months notice period or pay 6 months salary.
